%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-ngh%C4%A9-k%E1%BB%B7-c%C3%B4ng-bi-v%C4%83n-c%C3%A1nh-v%C3%B4-s%E1%BB%9F-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-nh%C3%A2n-ph%C3%BA-d%C4%A9-th%E1%BB%8B/poem-A2xkdK7IB0vtBKx0Ta6EFQ">Tái vị nhân đại nghĩ kỷ công bi văn cánh vô sở đắc nhân phú dĩ thị - 再為人代擬紀功碑文更無所得因賦以示</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/T%E1%BB%91ng-Kh%C3%BAc-Th%E1%BA%ADp-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-R4iaGG8DCqemexlSGFxz1g">Tống Khúc Thập thiếu phủ - 送麴十少府</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-3mvgQ8jqLVNdE0oNQACUCg">Vịnh hoài kỳ 2 - 詠懷其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-S%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/X%C3%ADch-B%C3%ADch-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-bT4GIPnEJSxYYBPIGRxl0g">Xích Bích đồ - 赤壁圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-S%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-xomLzH62F_NkzLMPyZ81UA">Ngô Sư Đạo</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
